designed for educational purposes, software engineering demonstration, and
AI/ML research exploration. Specifically:

  • This Software does NOT constitute financial, investment, tax, legal,
    or regulatory advice of any kind.

  • The predictions, scores, signals, and analysis outputs generated by
    this Software are the product of machine learning models trained on
    historical data, and are subject to significant uncertainty, bias,
    and error.

  • Past performance indicators used in training or analysis do not
    guarantee future results.

  • Users who deploy or consume this Software in any financial decision-
    making context do so entirely at their own risk.

  • Users are solely responsible for compliance with applicable financial
    regulations, licensing requirements, data privacy laws (including GDPR,
